 Boards & Committees



Corporate Boards ▾




Independent Director

                    2011 - Current                  


Conmed Healthcare Management, Inc.

                    Conmed Healthcare Management, Inc. provides correctional healthcare services to county and municipal detention centers across the United States. It offers various services, including general healthcare, dialysis, pharmacy, acute care, EKG's, durable medical equipment, physical and occupational therapy, IV therapy, and diagnostic imaging/radiology. The firm also offers laboratory, dental, mental health, electronic medical records, arranging and contracting for hospital and surgical, electronic medication administration records, and utilization management and utilization review services. Conmed Healthcare Management was founded by Ronald H. Grubman and Howard M. Haft in 1984 and is headquartered in Hanover, MD.                  




Director

                    Current                  


The National Collaborative for Bio-Preparedness






Independent Director

                    2009 - Prior                  


PharmAthene, Inc.

                    PharmAthene, Inc. (NYSE Amex: PIP), formed in March 2001 is pursuing its mission to become the premier company worldwide specializing in the development and rapid commercialization of best-in-class medical countermeasures for the multi-billion dollar biodefense industry. By following a strategy of acquiring leading compounds and technologies focused only on high priority medical countermeasures solutions identified by the United States and other governments as urgent to procure, PharmAthene has built a solid product pipeline and a strong reputation within the industry.                  





